{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/gatsby-learning/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jason Yang's Website","author":"Jason Yang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"286b2e51-e4d7-5e34-9b47-96b032104e37","excerpt":"什么是 Gatsby Gatsby是一个基于React的免费开源的静态网站生成框架，可以快速构建网站和APP。 为什么用 Gatsby 基于 React 插件丰富 静态文件 速度飞快 Gatsby …","html":"<h3 id=\"什么是-gatsby\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF-gatsby\" aria-label=\"什么是 gatsby permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>什么是 Gatsby</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/\">Gatsby</a>是一个基于React的免费开源的静态网站生成框架，可以快速构建网站和APP。</p>\n<h3 id=\"为什么用-gatsby\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%94%A8-gatsby\" aria-label=\"为什么用 gatsby permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>为什么用 Gatsby</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>基于 React</li>\n<li>插件丰富</li>\n<li>静态文件</li>\n<li>速度飞快</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"gatsby-环境准备\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gatsby-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87\" aria-label=\"gatsby 环境准备 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gatsby 环境准备</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>安装 <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/\">nodejs</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装 <code>gatsby-cli</code></p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"shell\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">npm install --global gatsby-cli</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装 git</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>选个顺手的代码编辑器，推荐使用 <a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\">vs code</a></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"使用-gatsby-starters\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-gatsby-starters\" aria-label=\"使用 gatsby starters permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用 Gatsby starters</h3>\n<p>Gatsby 提供了一些 starter 以便快速构建网站，这些 starter 在他们的 <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs\">github</a> 上，通过<code>gatsby new</code>命令，可以基于 starter 创建一个本地 Gatsby 网站。</p>\n<p>使用以下命令可以基于 <code>gatsby-starter-hello-world</code> starter 创建一个 Gatsby 网站。</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"shell\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">gatsby new hello-world https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-hello-world</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>项目创建完后，进入<code>hello-word</code> 目录，执行 <code>gatsby develop</code> 来启动项目，默认端口号为<code>8000</code>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"认识-gatsby-的页面\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86-gatsby-%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2\" aria-label=\"认识 gatsby 的页面 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>认识 Gatsby 的页面</h3>\n<p>在编辑器中打开<code>src/pages/index.js</code>，该文件中的代码表示创建了一个组件，该组件包含一个div和字符串”hello world”。</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">import React from &quot;react&quot;\n\nexport default () =&gt; &lt;div&gt;Hello world!&lt;/div&gt;</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>in pure javascript:</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">import React from &quot;react&quot;\n\nexport default () =&gt; React.createElement(&quot;div&quot;, null, &quot;Hello world!&quot;)</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"components\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#components\" aria-label=\"components permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Components</h3>\n<p>一个组件是网站的构建块，是一段自包含的代码，描述了UI的一部分。Gatsby 是基于React 编写的。当我们谈使用和定义组件时，实际上是在说React组件——自包含的代码片段(通常使用JSX编写)，它可以接受输入并返回描述UI部分的React元素。</p>\n<p>原生的HTML定义一个button</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"html\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">&lt;button class=&quot;primary-button&quot;&gt;Click me&lt;/button&gt;</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>在React中，可以定义一个button组件，来替代原生的button</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"html\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">&lt;PrimaryButton&gt;Click me&lt;/PrimaryButton&gt;</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h4 id=\"sub-component\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sub-component\" aria-label=\"sub component permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>sub-component</h4>\n<p>在<code>src/components</code>目录下新建一个<code>header.js</code></p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">import React from &quot;react&quot;\n\nexport default () =&gt; &lt;h1&gt;This is a header.&lt;/h1&gt;</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>在<code>src/pages</code>目录下新建一个<code>about.js</code>，引入Header组件</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">import React from &quot;react&quot;\nimport Header from &quot;../components/header&quot;\n\nexport default () =&gt; (\n  &lt;div style={{ color: `teal` }}&gt;\n    &lt;Header /&gt; \n    &lt;p&gt;Such wow. Very React.&lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;\n)</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>如果想让header的文本支持自定义，需要修改header.js成如下：</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">import React from &quot;react&quot;\n\nexport default props =&gt; &lt;h1&gt;{props.headerText}&lt;/h1&gt;</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>然后在about.js中，指定headerText属性的值即可</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">import React from &quot;react&quot;\nimport Header from &quot;../components/header&quot;\n\nexport default () =&gt; (\n  &lt;div style={{ color: `teal` }}&gt;\n    &lt;Header headerText=&quot;About Gatsby&quot; /&gt; \n    &lt;p&gt;Such wow. Very React.&lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;\n)</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"props\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#props\" aria-label=\"props permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Props</h3>\n<p>想要让这些可重用的组件具有动态性，能够为它们赋值，就可以使用 props 来完成此操作。props 是 React components 提供的属性。</p>\n<p>在上面的例子中，我们通过 <code>headerText=\"About Gatsby\"</code> 来引入<code> Header</code> sub-component</p>\n<h3 id=\"link\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#link\" aria-label=\"link permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Link</h3>\n<h4 id=\"使用-link-组件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-link-%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"使用 link 组件 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用 &#x3C;Link/> 组件</h4>\n<p>修改index.js</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">import React from &quot;react&quot;\nimport { Link } from &quot;gatsby&quot;\nimport Header from &quot;../components/header&quot;\n\nexport default () =&gt; (\n    &lt;div style={{ color: &#39;teal&#39;}}&gt;\n        &lt;Link to=&quot;/contact/&quot;&gt;Contact&lt;/Link&gt;\n        &lt;Header headerText=&quot;Hello Gatsby!&quot;/&gt;\n        &lt;p&gt;what is this...&lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n)</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>新建一个contact.js</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">import React from &quot;react&quot;\nimport { Link } from &quot;gatsby&quot;\nimport Header from &quot;../components/header&quot;\n\nexport default () =&gt; (\n    &lt;div style={{ color: &#39;teal&#39;}}&gt;\n        &lt;Link to=&quot;/contact/&quot;&gt;Contact&lt;/Link&gt;\n        &lt;Header headerText=&quot;Contact&quot;/&gt;\n        &lt;p&gt;you can follow me on github&lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n)</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"小结\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93\" aria-label=\"小结 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>小结</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>了解 Gatsby</li>\n<li>Gatsby 环境准备</li>\n<li>使用 Gatsby starters 创建网站</li>\n<li>JSX 语法</li>\n<li>Components</li>\n<li>Gatsby page components 和 sub-components</li>\n<li>React “props” 和重用 React components</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF-gatsby\">什么是 Gatsby</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%94%A8-gatsby\">为什么用 Gatsby</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#gatsby-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87\">Gatsby 环境准备</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-gatsby-starters\">使用 Gatsby starters</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86-gatsby-%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2\">认识 Gatsby 的页面</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#components\">Components</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#sub-component\">sub-component</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#props\">Props</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#link\">Link</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-link-%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6\">使用 &#x3C;Link/> 组件</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93\">小结</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby 入门","tags":["coding"],"description":"Gatsby是个好东西，这玩意用了上瘾。","date":"2019-05-27"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/gatsby-learning/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/java-garbage-collection/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Java 垃圾收集器","tags":["coding"],"slug":""}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/graph-algorithms/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"常用的图算法","tags":["coding"],"slug":""}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2052298874"],"slicesMap":{}}